[
  {
    "text": "论文越看越多，新闻越刷越多，聊天记录也越来越长。",
    "startMs": 0,
    "endMs": 4371,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "但真正的问题是：信息都看过，却很难记住，也很难串起来。",
    "startMs": 4371,
    "endMs": 9289,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "所以，我把自己研究方法提炼成skill做成了一套 pipeline。",
    "startMs": 9289,
    "endMs": 15300,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "它叫 PaperTrace。",
    "startMs": 15300,
    "endMs": 17208,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "它会把论文、新闻和对话放进pipeline中，",
    "startMs": 17208,
    "endMs": 20584,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "帮我整理来源、核对信息，",
    "startMs": 20584,
    "endMs": 22345,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "也记住我已经理解了什么、还没掌握什么。",
    "startMs": 22345,
    "endMs": 25133,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "你把一篇 PDF 放进去，它会自动整理成双语阅读页面。",
    "startMs": 25133,
    "endMs": 29473,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "每一段重点、每一个公式、每一张图，都能随时找到原文出处。",
    "startMs": 29473,
    "endMs": 34333,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "通过维护个人知识库，帮你顺着一条线继续读下去，",
    "startMs": 34333,
    "endMs": 38843,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "而不是看完一篇就散了。除了论文，它也会同步核实最新资讯。",
    "startMs": 38843,
    "endMs": 44333,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "比如 Anthropic 的动态、IBM Quantum 的进展，",
    "startMs": 44333,
    "endMs": 48958,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "以及 arXiv 上的新论文。搜索结果只负责提供线索，",
    "startMs": 48958,
    "endMs": 52944,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "最终结论必须由官方来源和原始论文来证明。",
    "startMs": 52944,
    "endMs": 56133,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "更重要的是，PaperTrace 不会把“你看过”当成“你学会了”。",
    "startMs": 56133,
    "endMs": 61731,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "只有当你明确表示理解、纠正或确认后，",
    "startMs": 61731,
    "endMs": 64784,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "它才会更新你的学习记录。",
    "startMs": 64784,
    "endMs": 66820,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "论文、新闻、对话，三种信息入口，最后都进入同一套记忆。",
    "startMs": 66820,
    "endMs": 71400,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "让你今天看到的内容，不会明天又从头开始。",
    "startMs": 71400,
    "endMs": 74493,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "PaperTrace，让每一次阅读，",
    "startMs": 74493,
    "endMs": 77277,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  },
  {
    "text": "都成为下一次研究的起点。",
    "startMs": 77277,
    "endMs": 79133,
    "timestampMs": null,
    "confidence": null
  }
